{"tid":1804302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！必須盡快光復連儂牆！","createTime":"2019-12-31T01:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T03:32:48.000Z","uid":51314,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b1e0bffe6d9462733b237965a0054a0d3fa312","tid":1804302,"uid":51314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"連儂牆的重要性十分大，它可以連結社區既同路人，亦能使資訊跳出同溫層，俾更多人看到（好似叔叔姨姨真係會停低睇），更重要的是它將大家都知但扮唔知既事實公開咁講，逼香港人不能扮唔知、沉默。<br />\n只是現在政府同武裝分子強力打擊，又地下化咁捉人，令到貼文宣既手足都好頭痕。面對打壓，我地都要諗諗計，盡快光復連儂牆！<br />\nEnzo Mazak都俾左啲建議，大家可以參考下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mw5YamY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmw5YamY.png&h=829a7a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wr0pQm0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwr0pQm0.png&h=e915d083&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYCWGtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYCWGtH.png&h=717ac8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1210835166605664256?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1210835166605664256%3Fs%3D20&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=a751200d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1210835166605664256%3Fs%3D20&h=682e9be3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1210835166605664256?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"2fa96f6b7c9e7a489b93c3e628d819bab826deda","tid":1804302,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c4a4b04e5aa7ac6c2803101f3b4e3e36617a308","tid":1804302,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:46:47.000